{"title":"InternationElles’ Fundraiser for Equal Payout for the Women’s Peloton","link":"https://theradavist.com/2021/03/internationelles-fundraiser-for-equal-payout-for-the-womens-peloton/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=internationelles-fundraiser-for-equal-payout-for-the-womens-peloton","date":1614707639000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><section><article id=\"article-206519\"><div><p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/EqualPay.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" alt=\"InternationElles’ Fundraiser for Equal Payout for the Women’s Peloton\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/EqualPay.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w,https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/EqualPay.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/EqualPay.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2021/03/EqualPay.jpg\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/EqualPay.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w,https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/EqualPay.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/EqualPay.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"></p></div><header><h4>Radar</h4></header><div><p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/EqualPay.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/EqualPay.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/EqualPay.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/EqualPay.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/EqualPay.jpg\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/EqualPay.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/EqualPay.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/EqualPay.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"></p><p>It’s 2021 and women’s cycling is still fighting for their equal piece of the pie, as illustrated here by artist <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/thomas_slater/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Thomas Slater</a>. The InternationElles have had enough. These ten female cyclists and three crews from across the globe, are united in the fight for equality. Their hope is through activism, that they can boost women’s cycling. Right now, they have a <a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/equal-prize-money-for-the-womens-peloton\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GoFundMe</a> to raise €5,000&nbsp;as equal prize money to the top 5 women’s podium for the upcoming 2021 Strade Bianche. The above illustration might seem like an exaggeration but the <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CL1jDUKFH8Q/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">payout at the recent Omloop Het Nieuwsblad</a> paints a clear and concise picture…</p><p>Hopefully, the UCI, USAC, and other organizations will get with the times.</p></div><nav><h4>Related</h4></nav></article></section></div>","author":"prolly","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"898c3348824839cf0ae1b93c722262cc16d69ac09d2f434840aeac7b36896809","category":"Cycling"}